,858],"class_list":["post-17337","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","hentry","category-quran-exegesis-tafsir","tag-calamity-al-museebah","tag-discouraged-al-makruh","tag-ease-al-yusr","tag-good-deeds-hasanat","tag-hardship","tag-manners-adab","tag-monotheism-tawhid","tag-patience-sabr","tag-providence-al-qada-wal-qadr","tag-success-al-falah","tag-surah-al-sharh"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-4vD","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":40167,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/18\/usri-yusrayn\/","url_meta":{"origin":17337,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ease: Difficulty decreed along with two reliefs","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Qatadah ibn Di\u2019amatah reported: It has been mentioned to us that the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, gave glad tidings to his companions about this verse, \u201cVerily, with the hardship comes an ease, with the hardship comes an ease,\u201d (94:5-6) and the Prophet said, \u201cA hardship\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40165,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/18\/maa-usri-yusra\/","url_meta":{"origin":17337,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ease: Difficulty certain to be followed by relief","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, was once standing over a hole and he said, \u201cIf hardship were to enter this hole, ease would surely follow it, go inside, and take it out.\u201d Then, Allah Almighty revealed the verse, \u201cVerily, with the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37727,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/02\/23\/prophets-rejoice-hardship\/","url_meta":{"origin":17337,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Trials: Prophets rejoice at hardship, seeking reward","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 23, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe most severely tested are the Prophets, and then the righteous. One of them would be tested with poverty until he could find nothing to cover himself but a cloak. One of them would rejoice\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36609,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/06\/sabr-unless-disobedient\/","url_meta":{"origin":17337,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Rulers: Patience with tyranny but no obedience in sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"\u2018Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cListen and obey authorities in hardship, in ease, and in what you dislike, even if they give undue preference over you, even if they consume your property and they strike your back, unless they order\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39799,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/19\/ibn-masud-qadr\/","url_meta":{"origin":17337,"position":4},"title":"Abdullah on Qadr: Accept Allah\u2019s decree with patience or gratitude","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Qays ibn Khabtar reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cAccept two things you dislike: death and poverty. By Allah, there is nothing but richness and poverty, and I do not care with which of them I am put to trial, for the right of Allah\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39732,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/17\/patience-first-shock\/","url_meta":{"origin":17337,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Patience: Be calm at the first shock of calamity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPatience is at the first strike of calamity. Patience is at the first strike of calamity.\u201d Source: Musnad Abi\u0304 Ya\u2019la\u0301 6068 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u200c\u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\